									Язь. Leuciscus idus (L.) 							</h2>
				
		
				
			</div>


<div class="icons">
	
		
	</div>


		<dl class="article-info muted">

		
			<dt class="article-info-term">
									Подробности							</dt>

			
			
			
					
					
			
										<dd class="hits">
					<span class="icon-eye-open"></span>
					<meta itemprop="interactionCount" content="UserPageVisits:972" />
